block prepend article
  - var sectionId = "layout-flexbox-systems"
  - var sectionTitle = "Flexbox Systems"

block section
  
  p.
    Since Codebase 2.0, the flexbox layout mixins and classes formerly using the word "grid" have been renamed simply as layout #[code flexbox] and "col" (column) has been renamed as #[code flexitem]. This has been done so that the word "grid" can instead be used in the names of mixins and classes to refer to the new CSS grid specification.

  table.table.deco
